                <h2>How to Get a Subdomain</h2>
                <p>- **Invite Friends**: Invite at least **5 active members** to the server.</p>
                <p>- **Boost the Server**: Server boosters are eligible for a subdomain.</p>
                <p>- **One-Time Payment**: Pay a **$3 one-time fee** for lifetime access to your subdomain if boosting or inviting isn't possible.</p>
