            <!-- Eligibility Requirements -->
            <div class="info-box">
                <h2>Eligibility Requirements</h2>
                <p>- You must remain an active member of the server.</p>
                <p>- Invited friends must stay active in the server. If your friends leave, your subdomain may be revoked.</p>
                <p>- If you unboost the server, your subdomain will be suspended until boosting is resumed.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Consequences -->
            <div class="info-box">
                <h2>What Happens If You No Longer Qualify?</h2>
                <p>- If you lose eligibility (e.g., friends leave, you unboost), your subdomain will be **suspended**.</p>
                <p>- To reinstate your subdomain, you must:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Re-invite friends to meet the minimum.</li>
                    <li>Reboost the server.</li>
                    <li>The $3 lifetime fee remains unaffected.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Rules -->
            <div class="info-box">
                <h2>Subdomain Rules & Usage</h2>
                <p>- Subdomains must follow all server rules and **Terms of Service**.</p>
                <p>- Misusing a subdomain (e.g., hosting prohibited content) will lead to immediate suspension and potential server ban.</p>
            </div>

